<a name="newsitem979543907,59542,"></a>
<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">GameZView Grand Opening</font> </strong><small>Posted Monday, January 15, 2001 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
I wanted to take the time to announce the grand opening of <a href="http://www.gamezview.com">GameZView</a>. GameZView is the latest addition to the GameZNet family of sites. That's all fine and dandy your saying but what does it do?<br><br>GameZView contains a search database which allows you to search for reviews, cheats, walkthroughs, developer pages, etc for your favorite software. It allows you to filter your searches not only by name but also by platform, genre and article type. We will be adding to this database daily from this point onward. GameZView also provides search boxes for instant searching of the advanced search engine at <a href="http://www.gamezportal.com">GameZPortal</a>, news archives from the <a href="http://www.gameznet.com">GameZNet</a> network and our large cheat database at <a href="http://www.gamezcheat.com">GameZCheat</a>. We feel that it should be a valuable resource when seeking information regarding the tommorrow's games. <br><br>Along with the addition of GameZView we have done a large update to our news service. News at GameZView and GameZNet are identical mirrors of one another and the headlines are still mirrored via news feed to GameZPortal. What we have added are advanced <a href="http://gamezview.com/categories.shtml">News Categories</a>, News Comments and Archived Searching. With these additions we will pledge a renewed emphasis on our gaming news coverage. We hope that you enjoy the service.<br><br>Cheers!<br><br>New 1HBlunts: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/etchedveliumbattlehammer.html">Etched Velium Battlehammer</a>.<br>New Helms: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/sorcerorscirclet.html">Sorcerer's Circlet</a>(WIZ).<br>New Boots: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/bootsofstability.html">Boots of Stability</a>(CLR).<br>New Arms: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/vambracesofstability.html">Vambraces of Stability</a>(CLR).<br>New Gloves: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/sorcerorsgloves.html">Sorceror's Gloves</a>(WIZ).<br>New Necklaces: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/talismanofvhalsera.html">Talisman of Vhal Sera</a>.<br>New Masks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/maskofthedragonslayer.html">Mask of the Dragon Slayer</a>.<br>New Shields: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/shieldofthefreezingwinds.html">Shield of the Freezing Winds</a>.<br>New Held Items: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/crystalrodofconfusion.html">Crystal Rod of Confusion</a>(ENC).
</p>
