<p><strong><font color="#f0f0f0">Quests and Equipment</font> </strong><small>Posted Thursday, January 11, 2001 by <a href="mailto:jcsmith@gameznet.com">jcsmith</a></small><br>
Here's a doseage of quests and equipment to make up for yesterday. The third reward of the Sifaye Battlegrounds quest is included in this update as well as a new drop from Dain Frostreaver.<br><br>Yesterday's broken images will be fixed in about an hour(heading there now). They are likely fixed by the time you are reading this. =)<br><br>New 2HSlashs: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/vinidcation.html">Vindication</a>.<br>New Robes: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/sorcerorsrobe.html">Sorceror's Robe</a>(WIZ).<br>New Helmets: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/archmagescrown.html">Arch Mage's Crown</a>(MAG), <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/spiritweaverscoif.html">Spirit Weaver's Coif</a>(SHM).<br>New Gloves: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/coldaindskingloves.html">Coldain Skin Gloves</a>, <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/thunderetchedgauntlets.html">Thunder Etched Gauntlets</a>.<br>New Cloaks: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/frostreaversembroideredcloak.html">Frostreaver's Embroirdered Cloak</a>.<br>New Earrings: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/helssensprismatictrinket.html">Helssen's Prismatic Trinket</a>.<br>New Held Items: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/equipment/fluteofthesacredglade.html">Flute of the Sacred Glade</a>(BRD).<br>New Kael Quests: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/quest/icewellassassinations.html">Icewell Assassinations</a>.<br>Updated Kael Quests: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/quest/gleedsbow.html">Gleed's Bow</a>.<br>Updated Thurgadin Quests: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/quest/thurgadinmagician.html">Thurgadin Magician Armor</a>(MAG).<br>Updated Wakening Land Quests: <a href="http://gameznet.com/eq/quest/sifayebattlegrounds.html">Sifaye Battlegrounds</a>.
